that these scripts download and install. Those projects are subject to their
own respective licenses.

---

These scripts are intended to enable Windows-based Winlink applications to run
on Linux and macOS via Wine. Supported applications include those available at
downloads.winlink.org.

The following software has not been tested and is not currently supported by
these scripts:

  - SCS USB Driver 2.08.24 WHQL Certified
    (downloads.winlink.org - /Sysop Programs/SCS USB Driver 2.08.24 WHQL Certified/)

Note: USB kernel drivers such as the above are not compatible with Wine and
require a native Windows environment or a dedicated Windows virtual machine.
